Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_ptp_clock_comp

This register provides the amount to increment the PTP clock [MIO_PTP_CLOCK_HI, MIO_PTP_CLOCK_LO] on PTP events defined by MIO_PTP_CLOCK_CFG[EXT_CLK_EN/EXT_CLK_IN/EXT_CLK_EDGE]. MIO_PTP_CLOCK_CFG[PTP_EN] needs to be enabled before writing this register.
